==Standings==
{{2026 FIFA World Cup group tables|Group J}}

In the [[2026 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Round of 32|round of 32]]:<ref name="regulations"/>
* The winner of Group J will advance to play the runner-up of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group H|Group H]].
* The runner-up of Group J will advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group H|Group H]].
* The third-placed team of Group J might advance to play the winner of [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group B|Group B]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group D|Group D]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group G|Group G]], [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group K|Group K]], or [[2026 FIFA World Cup Group L|Group L]] (if one of the [[2026 FIFA World Cup#Ranking of third-placed teams|eight best third-placed teams]] from the group stage).

